Controls : A And D to move and Space bar to jump. Click at the card to close. To save, press control key. To load, press "tab". During the boss battle, press J to shoot nasi lemak at enemy.

Embark on a thrilling journey across Malaysia with Tigar,a fearless tiger explorer, on an epic journey through Malaysia! In this colorful platformer, dash through iconic landscapes  from city streets to lush rainforests  while collecting special Malaysia Culture Cards that reveal fun facts about the countrys rich heritage. But beware! The evil gorilla Obarok the Colossal - an old enemy of Tigar, has sent his toxic Rafflesia minions to stop you. Avoid enemies, and get ready for a final boss battle showdown to save Malaysias culture.
Will Tigar restore cultural harmony and defeat Obarok once and for all!?
  The adventure awaits!
